                    <div class="section-title text-left">
                        <span class="section-title__tagline editable">What is a Tin Cup Challenger?</span>
                        <h2 class="section-title__title editable">Tin Cup Challengers</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p class="about-three__text-1 editable">Challengers are a special group of individuals and businesses who donate to the Challenger Fund. These gifts are not earmarked for specific nonprofits, but are used to match the community's donations. Challengers generously give at levels of $1,000+.</p>
                    <p class="about-three__text-2 editable">Challengers' generosity inspires increased community giving and is key to Tin Cup's success. Challengers can proudly call themselves community leaders who promote charitable giving and intrinsically value philanthropy. Combined with community-wide efforts, they highlight the tremendous work of local nonprofits and appreciation of that work.</p>
                    <a href="/challengers/" class="thm-btn about-three__btn editable">Tin Cup Challengers</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
