                        <h2 class="section-title__title editable">In-Kind Donors</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p class="about-three__text-1 editable">Tin Cup relies on the generosity of dozens of local businesses and nonprofits that donate goods and services to the event.</p>
                    <h3 class="about-three__subtitle editable">The Shirt Off Their Back Givers</h3>
                    <p class="about-three__text-2 editable">It is with deep gratitude that we recognize and celebrate our Tin Cup Challenge In-Kind Donors. Their generous discounts and local services keep our production costs low so that more Challenger dollars can be invested back into our community.</p>
